40 calendar days, which can be reduced by 5 days, to no less than 25 days, for each of the following conditions: the NPP is published electronically all tender documents are available electronically from the NPP date of publication the procuring entity accepts tenders electronically Note: If using limited tendering, the solicitation period should be at least 15 calendar days.",
